  m_Name: WodeWoBaby
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: KyndeBlade.Core::KyndeBlade.StoryBeat
  BeatId: WodeWoBaby
  Text: "A softe somer morwen on Malvern Hilles. Wille resteth bynethe the Worcestershire
    Beacon. \"In a somer seson, whan softe was the sonne...\" Slep cometh. The drem
    bygynneth.\n\nIn the schade of an elde ook, Wille findeth a litel thyng\u2014mos
    and leef, rote and bark, no grettere than a fust. A sedlyng. A child of the wode.
    It stireth, rechyng after warmth. His breth is feynt, as wynd thurgh yonge leves."
  SpeakerName: Narrator
  Portrait: {fileID: 0}
  DisplayDuration: 8
  WaitForInput: 1
  VisionIndex: 0
  PassusIndex: 0
